Strings
-------

Strings in templates are either enclosed by ' or " and are only allowed as parameters
for macros and methods.

..  source: html

    <!-- allowed -->
    {{write("testtext")}}
    {{write('testtext')}}
    
    <!-- forbidden -->
    {{"testtext"}}
    {{'testtext'}}

