+---------------+-----------+-----------+-----------------------------------------------+
| $b            | mixed     | -         | optional amount for decreasing (default: 1)   |
+---------------+-----------+-----------+-----------------------------------------------+

    _Example:_

    ..  source: html

        <!-- output: 5 - 2 = 3 -->
        {{decr(5, 2)}}


